__e: But justice don't change nowhere... even in places where they give medals for killin' Indians, like out here.
But you can't change what you did.
No matter what happens tomorrow, that won't change.
The entire balance of power in the world about to shift, 2 guys can still have a stare-down over who gets the girl.
Only by confronting our fears are we able to grow, to change, and to be able to face our next.
Then I saw younger Rip change, and I thought, why not give it a shot?
I wish I could change it, but I can't.
And it was stupid to think that you could change.
You'd be amazed what can change in a week in my bed.
